  <script language="javascript" type="text/javascript">
      var stri = window.parent.location.href;
      var strii = stri.indexOf('?');
      if (strii != -1) {
          var indexe = stri.substring(stri.indexOf('=') + 1);
          var pagename = indexe.substring(indexe.indexOf('/') + 1);
          window.location.href = '../index.html#PageName=' + pagename;
      }
     
  </script>
<body>
<div id="country3" class="tabcontent">

<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">
<h2>Bed Master</h2><hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen captures the ward bed details. 
<br /><hr /><br />
<img src="images/mst_BedMaster.jpg" width="725" /><br /><br />
<hr />

<p>

<span class="title">Bed Number: </span><br />
On the basis of the search requirement, user can choose Bed Number.
<br />
  <span class="title">Textbox and Search (Button): </span> 
    <br />Textbox is to write the value you are searching or looking for. Once it's done you can click on search button to get the result of your search. 
<br />
    <span class="title">GRID (Display): </span> 
    <br />Based on search criteria data will display in the form of table. At a time only five records will be displayed. To navigate or look for the next record pagination (the system of numbering pages) will be there. 
<br />
    <span class="title">Go Button and Text Box : </span> 
    <br />If user wants to switch directly to any particular page no., the he can simply enter the page no. in the given text box and click on Go Button.
<br />
    <span class="title">Bed Number: </span> 
    <br />User can write bed number , it can't remain blank. 
<br />
    <span class="title">Ward Name: </span> 
    <br />User can select the ward name from the given list, this will come from department screen, it can't remain blank.
          All ward names will display based on department type is ‘ward’.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Room Number: </span> 
    <br />User can select the room number from the given list, this will come from room type screen, it can't remain blank.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Bed Status:  </span> 
    <br />User can select the bed status from the given list, this will come from bed status screen, it can't remain blank.
    <br />
    <span class="title">AD Number: </span> 
    <br />If user is admitted particular bed automatically AD number will come against bed.
    <br />
    <span class="title">Diet Type:  </span> 
    <br />User can select diet type from the given list, it contains Veg and Non-Veg.
    <br />
    <span class="title">Attached: </span> 
    <br />User can select attached required for bed or not.
    
    
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Save (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on Save button user can save the data. 
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Update (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on Update button user can modify the existing data.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Inactive (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on inactive button user can inactive the existing data.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Reset (Button):</span> 
    <br />Clicking on reset button, will clear the current or existing data. 
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Back (Button):</span> 
    <br />Clicking on Back button, will move user to the previous screen.
           
</p>

</div>
</body>
</html>
